{"tid":1708132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新亞中學某中六學生：罷課冇意思 黎明行動冇意義 miss請繼續教書 我要上堂","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T13:37:01.000Z","uid":292384,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83ee0a1cd359efdce9eec6544f48786589462ccb","tid":1708132,"uid":292384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEUnFN3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEUnFN3.jpg&h=28ececa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">［幫朋友代po］</span>件事係咁嘅 今日 1111全港幾乎間間學校都搞緊罷課之際 某支那新亞學生突然變得好學 叫Miss繼續教書 重溫中國語文12篇章<span style=\"color: red;\">（但平時條友係冇咁好學㗎 功課都唔係準時交果批 唔知點解突然今日搞緊罷課之際變得咁好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</span><br />\n跟住翻到學校之後 條友同人講其實全港學校搞罷課根本就無意義 其他人話要罷課 佢就話我要繼續上堂 佢仲講補充左句D手足去支援黎明行動更加冇意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大概過咗一段時間後 某個黃絲同學睇緊今日交通警連開三槍嘅片段嗰陣 佢又突然間變黃 話個交通警草菅人命之餘此類嘅説話 完完全全係一個偽黃絲黎 喺度扮晒嘢 真係變藍又得 變黃又得 以為自己係荷蘭叻咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係班黃絲面前就係咁講popo衰嘢 係背後就話我哋班手足做嘅嘢冇意義 罷課亦都無意思 真係忍唔住要開post屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n各位手足千奇唔好打佢電話啊 人哋拎綜緩好慘㗎 我驚佢成日買潮鞋冇錢換電話卡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d682f57f9f885852d0ca87ac7e76e23aacd4dcb2","tid":1708132,"uid":251945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"咁小野就唔好po上黎啦，自己私了左去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a407ec16e1bcad101cf715bcba004dc9df688be","tid":1708132,"uid":38420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"屌 對唔對得住中大新亞手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4ff964409beedb4f540be3ad0ef11986533453","tid":1708132,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a407ec16e1bcad101cf715bcba004dc9df688be","tid":1708132,"uid":38420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:18:26.000Z","msg":"屌 對唔對得住中大新亞手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"不嬲家陣新亞都係幾乎全部都係支那仔黎 只在乎自己嘅利益家咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1d96d6c951ed8b2cbb9428fb1f27046bbe264a","tid":1708132,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d682f57f9f885852d0ca87ac7e76e23aacd4dcb2","tid":1708132,"uid":251945,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:17:22.000Z","msg":"咁小野就唔好po上黎啦，自己私了左去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"聽人講條友為人相當謹慎 好少會去發夢嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要私了佢有啲難度 不過大家可以打個電話提佢起身屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e2480e1f6767dee4cc22c684e9271aede1cafe","tid":1708132,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:24:50.000Z","msg":"電話：<span style=\"color: red;\">5703 9435</span>"},{"pid":"97961743a5fd3aee5e4f564f2610afe7b44b2937","tid":1708132,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"215a0fcb39ef128a12a8390f4e2d2c0f4cf961c7","tid":1708132,"uid":292384,"like":